Package: msxtractor
Type: Package
Title: Simple XIC and MS2 Extraction from mzML/mzXML Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Amir", family = "Sakhteman", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "amir@example.com")
Description: Small helper functions for extracting extracted ion chromatograms (XICs) from MS1 data and MS2 spectra matching a target precursor m/z from mzML or mzXML files using MSnbase.
